These eco settings can be adjusted using the Easy Printer Manager.', 'feature_11': 'Samsung MobilePrint application helps employees wirelessly print from their mobile devices. After downloading the application, the mobile device automatically detects nearby, compatible Samsung printers. feature details: {'feature_0': 'The elegant celestial blue colour makes it look sophisticated. This asymmetrically designed laptop also has a spun-metal finish and an ErgoLift hinge. This hinge lets the keyboard to tilt (5.5°) efficiently. Therefore, you can type with ease and comfort. It even delivers high-quality cooling and audio performance.', 'feature_1': 'It comes with ASUS’s ScreenPad Plus feature which will heighten your on-the-go computing experience. This full-width secondary touchscreen works jointly with the 35.56 cm (14) FHD display. As a result, you can utilise it thoroughly to customise and upgrade your workflow. It comes with efficient inbuilt apps. For example, you can use Quick Key to automate keyboard sequences with just a single tap. You can also take advantage of Handwriting to fill text in an intuitive way. It features App Switcher, Task Swap, and ViewMax too. These quick controls ensure that the interaction between ScreenPad Plus and the main display keeps flowing intuitively and seamlessly. If you want to open several tasks, you can use the Task Group feature. It will let you access multiple things with a simple touch. What’s more, if you want more area on the main display to work better, you can drag and drop apps or in-app toolbars on ScreenPad Plus.', 'feature_2': 'It comes with an active stylus which you can use on the ergonomically built ScreenPad Plus feature. You can utilise your creative ideas to draw or write on this stable platform. You can even accurately edit graphics on it.', 'feature_3': 'ScreenPad Plus lets you multitask between apps seamlessly. ASUS has also collaborated with third-party developers such as Corel (video editing software developer) to enhance the functioning of the ScreenPad Plus feature so that your productivity gets a significant boost.', 'feature_4': 'It comes with the powerful 10th Gen Intel Core i7-10510U processor. As a result, it delivers fast and optimal performance which can help you enhance your creativity. Its spacious SSD storage further upgrades its functioning. Also, its NVIDIA GeForce MX250 graphics card ensures that the displayed content appears clear and vivid.', 'feature_5': 'It has multiple cores, so it handles apps on the screen as well as on ScreenPad Plus effectively and with ease. It also ensures that your cross-screen workflow stays seamless.', 'feature_6': 'Thanks to the NVIDIA GeForce MX250 graphics chip, you can experience faster performance while using this laptop for work and entertainment. Also, if you use photo and video editing applications, you will be able to use them at high speeds. It even ensures seamless gaming. And since it is portable, you can take advantage of these features and create content on-the-go without any hassle.', 'feature_7': 'The four-sided frameless design of the FHD NanoEdge Display offers more screen space. As a result, you will get a captivating viewing experience. The displayed colours also appear vivid and accurate as it is PANTONE Validated.', 'feature_8': 'It has Windows Hello which lets you log in to your laptop easily and without any manual effort. To use it, all you need to do is simply glance at the infrared camera. It works in the dark too.', 'feature_9': 'It is equipped with efficient I/O ports, so you can enjoy seamless connectivity. Also, the Intel Wi-Fi 6 with Gig+ (802.11ax) lets you experience fast data speeds wirelessly.', 'feature_10': 'You can use Alexa to get your queries answered. You can even ask it to read you the current affairs, play songs, and so on. All you need to do is use your voice, and it will do the needful instantly. You can not only use it at home but also while you are travelling.', 'feature_11': 'The Golden Ear Team of ASUS has joined forces with Harman Kardon (audio experts) to let you experience high-quality audio. It features high-performing hardware and Smart Amplifier Technology. So, it offers clear and distortion-free sound. Also, it uses fine-tuned software to deliver power-packed sound.', 'feature_12': "It satisfies the MIL-STD-810G military standard of testing, and hence it is not just reliable but durable too. Also, along with ASUS's internal laptop tests, it has undergone extended tests. As a result, it can function smoothly in extreme altitudes, environments, temperatures, and humidities."}

The venting below will remain unaffected, thanks to the trapezoidal cut that carves out at the bottom of the screen.', 'feature_13': 'This gaming laptop is equipped with dual N-blade fans to enhance high airflow.
